Package: blockr.ui
Title: Cross-Cutting User Interface for the 'blockr' Ecosystem
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Granjon",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david@cynkra.com")
Description: Provides the cross-cutting user-interface surface used by
    'blockr'-flavoured Shiny apps: design tokens, base CSS, the block
    card, page chrome (app shell, navbar, options renderer), and a
    reusable sidebar primitive with a content registry. Designed to
    sit between 'blockr.core' and renderers such as 'blockr.dock', so
    extensions and embedded apps can adopt the look and feel without
    pulling in 'dockViewR'.
URL: https://bristolmyerssquibb.github.io/blockr.ui/
BugReports: https://github.com/BristolMyersSquibb/blockr.ui/issues
